external_knowledge:
- 'treasure troves of knowledge' refers to sites (s.site_name) where users complete challenges and earn points;
- 'gems earned' refers to the average points earned (AVG(cs.points_earned));
- 'the ultimate test' refers to the specific challenge (c.challenge_id = 1);
- 'braved the challenges numerous times' refers to users who have completed more than 5 challenges on the site (COUNT(up.completed_challenges) > 5).

sql:
SELECT AVG(score) AS average_score
FROM user_progress
WHERE site_id = 0 AND completed_challenges > 5;

SELECT difficulty, COUNT(*) AS challenge_count
FROM challenges
WHERE difficulty = 'hard';
